BEGIN_TEXT

Find a basis of the subspace of \({\mathbb R}^3\) defined by the equation \( $a x_1 + $b x_2 + $c x_3 = 0\). 
$BR
\{ mbox( ans_array(3,1,5), ', ', ans_array_extension(3,1,5), '.' ) \}  

END_TEXT

